snippet.title: ELEGIES Aya Trailer
snippet.description:
ELEGIES: Aya is a thriller visual novel planned for release in February 2023. 

The demo will be available on:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1977660/ELEGIES_Aya/
